25 toast; frozen scrambled egg mix in boilable pouches; frozen fried eggs; frozen
26 precooked scrambled eggs; freeze-dried scrambled eggs; ultra-pasteurized
27 liquid eggs; free-flowing frozen egg pellets; and specially coated shelf-stable
